Revision history for Task-BeLike-HMA

0.08_02 Jul 23, 2011

        - Reflect changes in LWP 6 to get SSL support
        - Test::Memory::Cycle requires Perl 5.8.2
        - Adjust required versions for many dependencies
        - Workaround for Module::CPANTS::Analyse requiring
          Test::YAML::Meta::Version (RT #65903)
        - Convert README to Markdown
        - Added modules
            * App::cpanlistchanges
            * App::cpanminus
            * App::cpanoutdated
            * App::pmuninstall
            * local::lib
        - Upgrade to Module::Install 1.01

0.08_01 Jan 24, 2011

        - Add Task::BeLike::HMA::Toolchain to metadata
        - Added modules
            * App::moduleshere
        - Add more Perl version checks for legacy Perls

0.08    Dec 15, 2010

        - Added modules
            * Carp::Always
            * Crypt::SSLeay
            * Data::Dump
        - Update Perl::Critic if required
        - Switch GitHub URLs to https

0.06    Oct 24, 2010

        - FIX: Re-enforced usage of CPAN.pm for installation

0.05    Oct 24, 2010

        - Module::Version requires Getopt::Long 2.36
        - Added modules
            * aliased
            * Carp::Clan
            * Config::General
            * Module::Install
            * Path::Class
            * Test::Memory::Cycle
            * Test::Requires

0.03    Oct 10, 2010

        - Made dependencies I use explicit
            * Archive::Zip
            * Parse::RecDescent
            * Sub::Exporter
        - Moved dependencies to Task-BeLike-HMA-Toolchain
            * Digest::MD5
            * File::Spec
            * Storable
            * Test::More
            * version.pm
        - Changed minimum Perl version to 5.6.1
        - Force Module::AutoInstall to use CPAN.pm
        - Installation order adjusted

0.01    Sep 12, 2010

        - Initial commit and release to GitHub
